<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 16:10:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>汉莎航空、瑞士航空和奥地利航空将以色列和中东航线的暂停期限延长至8月26日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/lufthansa-swiss-austrian-extend-suspension-of-israel-mideast-routes-until-august-26/00000191-6aff-dc6e-a991-ebfff4020000</link><description>汉莎航空集团还将取消德黑兰、贝鲁特、安曼和埃尔比勒的航班，并将避开伊朗和伊拉克领空，直至另行通知</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 15:32:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/lufthansa-swiss-austrian-extend-suspension-of-israel-mideast-routes-until-august-26/00000191-6aff-dc6e-a991-ebfff4020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列宗教犹太复国主义媒体发表专栏鼓励约旦河西岸的犹太人恐怖活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/religious-zionist-media-outlet-publishes-column-encouraging-jewish-terror-in-west-bank/00000191-6ab6-d876-a5ff-ebbe1aa40000</link><description>这篇题为“吉特和拉法命运相同”的文章是由右翼法律援助非政府组织的一位高级活动人士撰写的。它指的是周四西岸定居者袭击导致一名 23 岁巴勒斯坦人死亡的事件，并呼吁蓄意大规模屠杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 14:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/religious-zionist-media-outlet-publishes-column-encouraging-jewish-terror-in-west-bank/00000191-6ab6-d876-a5ff-ebbe1aa40000</guid></item><item><title>世界上每五个犹太人中就有一个是移民，比任何其他宗教团体都多</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/one-out-of-every-five-jews-in-the-world-is-a-migrant-more-than-any-other-religious-group/00000191-64d3-dab9-a7b9-f5d7e72e0000</link><description>皮尤研究中心的一项新研究发现，世界上 20% 的犹太人是移民，这使得他们比任何其他宗教团体的成员更有可能生活在出生地之外。以色列是世界上大多数犹太移民的首选目的地，也是首选原籍国</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 14:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/one-out-of-every-five-jews-in-the-world-is-a-migrant-more-than-any-other-religious-group/00000191-64d3-dab9-a7b9-f5d7e72e0000</guid></item><item><title>在呼吁“消灭加沙”后，国家检察官考虑对以色列巨星埃亚勒·戈兰进行刑事调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-mulls-probe-of-israeli-megastar-eyal-golan-for-calling-to-wipe-gaza-out/00000191-6a82-dda8-af9b-6fe244840000</link><description>一月份，国际法院在南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案中引用了戈兰的言论。戈兰的职业生涯面临着法律问题，包括因逃税和欺诈而被定罪，以及长期存在的针对未成年人的性犯罪指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 13:50:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-mulls-probe-of-israeli-megastar-eyal-golan-for-calling-to-wipe-gaza-out/00000191-6a82-dda8-af9b-6fe244840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近的无人机袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-drone-attack-near-border-with-lebanon/00000191-6a2a-d876-a5ff-eb2a33450000</link><description>周一，以色列消防部队努力扑灭以色列北部因无人机爆炸引发的大火。周日，黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 33 枚火箭弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-drone-attack-near-border-with-lebanon/00000191-6a2a-d876-a5ff-eb2a33450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列经济在加沙战争和地区紧张局势中艰难增长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-economy-struggles-to-grow-amid-war-in-gaza-regional-tensions/00000191-69ea-da30-a1b7-effa43150000</link><description>总体增长由消费者和政府支出以及固定资产投资的增长带动，抵消了出口 8.3% 的下降。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-economy-struggles-to-grow-amid-war-in-gaza-regional-tensions/00000191-69ea-da30-a1b7-effa43150000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的走狗改变了对哈马斯协议的态度，但他的极右翼盟友可能不会加入他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lackeys-change-tune-on-hamas-deal-but-his-far-right-allies-likely-wont-agree/00000191-66d0-d876-a5ff-e7f8454a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的喉舌在一周内突然改变了对与哈马斯释放人质协议的看法，这可能对谈判至关重要，但总理的极右翼盟友加入他们的可能性并不高</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lackeys-change-tune-on-hamas-deal-but-his-far-right-allies-likely-wont-agree/00000191-66d0-d876-a5ff-e7f8454a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙-埃及边境如何打破以色列-哈马斯协议僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/gazas-philadelphi-route-and-rafah-crossing-key-to-egypts-position-in-cease-fire-talks/00000191-671f-d1ca-adb9-6fff12880000</link><description>虽然以色列从加沙完全撤军不在停火谈判现阶段的议程上，但费城路线和加沙-西奈边境拉法过境点的地位对埃及的立场至关重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/gazas-philadelphi-route-and-rafah-crossing-key-to-egypts-position-in-cease-fire-talks/00000191-671f-d1ca-adb9-6fff12880000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡会见布林肯，美国敦促以色列和哈马斯实现加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article-live/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-67da-d3bf-a3b1-efff74eb0000</link><description>哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织声称对周日晚上的特拉维夫爆炸负责 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部：以色列国防军在约旦河西岸的炮火造成四人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军在约旦河西岸追捕杀害以色列保安人员的袭击者 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在加沙被火箭弹严重炸伤 ■ 拜登：我们不会放弃停火，这仍然是可能的</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 23:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article-live/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-67da-d3bf-a3b1-efff74eb0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最高法院，不到 5% 的法律职员不是犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/at-israels-supreme-court-less-than-5-percent-of-all-law-clerks-arent-jewish/00000191-670c-d772-a9d5-6fbcc3ae0000</link><description>以色列最高法院在过去两年半中授予了 134 名书记员职位。不到百分之五的学生被授予非犹太人——绝大多数人在特拉维夫大学或希伯来大学学习</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 22:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/at-israels-supreme-court-less-than-5-percent-of-all-law-clerks-arent-jewish/00000191-670c-d772-a9d5-6fbcc3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>在尼尔奥兹会议上，以色列人质的亲属要求商界领袖、公众采取行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/at-nir-oz-conference-hostages-relatives-demand-action-by-business-leaders-public/00000191-670c-d876-a5ff-e72cc18f0000</link><description>退休将军和商界领袖聚集在基布兹召开“全国紧急会议”，敦促内塔尼亚胡立即签署协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 20:51:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/at-nir-oz-conference-hostages-relatives-demand-action-by-business-leaders-public/00000191-670c-d876-a5ff-e72cc18f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织声称对特拉维夫爆炸负责，并发誓将发动更多自杀式袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/man-with-bomb-killed-in-tel-aviv-blast-police-shin-bet-probing-possible-terror-attack/00000191-6735-d3bf-a3b1-efb75b7f0000</link><description>特拉维夫莱希街发生爆炸，一名路人受伤，恐怖分子身亡 ■ 哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织声称对此次袭击负责 ■ 特拉维夫警察局长下令提高警戒级别，搜寻更多嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 20:42:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/man-with-bomb-killed-in-tel-aviv-blast-police-shin-bet-probing-possible-terror-attack/00000191-6735-d3bf-a3b1-efb75b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>对据称帮助平息父亲性侵犯案的以色列议员重新展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/probe-reopened-into-lawmaker-who-allegedly-helped-squelch-dads-sexual-assault-case/00000191-66d5-d3bf-a3b1-eff76eaf0000</link><description>国家检察官下令重新调查文化部副部长雅科夫·泰斯勒涉嫌收买其父亲的一名指控者</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 20:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/probe-reopened-into-lawmaker-who-allegedly-helped-squelch-dads-sexual-assault-case/00000191-66d5-d3bf-a3b1-eff76eaf0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示，美国关于加沙停火的新提议满足了内塔尼亚胡的新要求，阻碍了达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-new-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-66d7-d3bf-a3b1-eff7abd30000</link><description>哈马斯在多哈周末峰会以来的首份官方声明中指责内塔尼亚胡“设定新条件来破坏谈判”，并补充说新要求不符合释放安全囚犯的条件</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 19:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-new-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-66d7-d3bf-a3b1-eff7abd30000</guid></item><item><title>美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列，推动加沙协议恢复谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arrives-in-israel-to-push-for-gaza-deal-as-talks-resume/00000191-66a0-d3bf-a3b1-efb7adde0000</link><description>布林肯将与以色列官员举行会议，试图就与哈马斯的关键争论点达成谅解，谈判代表继续在埃及和卡塔尔举行会议</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 18:28:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arrives-in-israel-to-push-for-gaza-deal-as-talks-resume/00000191-66a0-d3bf-a3b1-efb7adde0000</guid></item><item><title>美国正在追捕以色列极右翼部长，他们对定居者的暴力表示欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-18/ty-article/.highlight/america-is-coming-for-israels-far-right-ministers-who-hail-settler-violence/00000191-65e6-dda8-af9b-65e6b4450000</link><description>定居者暴力持续不减的时间越长，后果就越严重，国际领导人采取自己的惩罚措施就越有道理</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 18:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-18/ty-article/.highlight/america-is-coming-for-israels-far-right-ministers-who-hail-settler-violence/00000191-65e6-dda8-af9b-65e6b4450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列保安人员在约旦河西岸袭击中被巴勒斯坦人杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-guard-killed-by-palestinian-in-west-bank-attack/00000191-6687-d772-a9d5-6ebf47430000</link><description>袭击者用锤子打死了38岁的吉迪恩·佩里，然后偷走了他的武器并驾车逃跑。以色列军队仍在追捕嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-guard-killed-by-palestinian-in-west-bank-attack/00000191-6687-d772-a9d5-6ebf47430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官将领导对定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄事件的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-investigation-into-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village/00000191-6669-deb0-ab91-f7fd846f0000</link><description>在对吉特的突袭中，一名巴勒斯坦人被枪杀，但没有逮捕任何人，国防机构的初步调查表明，预备役士兵可能在现场袖手旁观</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-investigation-into-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village/00000191-6669-deb0-ab91-f7fd846f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们之间有一堵冰墙”：罗宋汤地带的阿拉伯和犹太青少年结下了不解之缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/there-was-an-ice-wall-between-us-arab-and-jewish-teens-bond-in-the-borscht-belt/00000191-650d-d301-ad91-f57f9dfb0000</link><description>在卡茨基尔山度过一个夏天后，来自以色列的阿拉伯青少年回到了一个在战前很久就被种族隔离的动荡国家。组织者希望他们的对话能够产生影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/there-was-an-ice-wall-between-us-arab-and-jewish-teens-bond-in-the-borscht-belt/00000191-650d-d301-ad91-f57f9dfb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 317 天：以色列国家检察官将领导对约旦河西岸定居者骚乱的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-317-israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-probe-of-west-bank-settler-riot/00000191-6630-d398-a7f5-ff70f9370000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士告诉沙特日报《Al Sharq》，目前正在讨论的停火提案“完全违背”哈马斯 7 月同意的协议 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列愿意在谈判中的某些问题上保持灵活性 ■ 美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列，将于周一与内塔尼亚胡会面，讨论确保加沙停战的努力 ■ 这是战争开始 317 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:54:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-317-israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-probe-of-west-bank-settler-riot/00000191-6630-d398-a7f5-ff70f9370000</guid></item></channel></rss>